{
  "stem": "7069.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was an imposing figure.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then we met some of the, some of the artists.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were several singers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was a-- it doesn't mean anything nowadays anymore-- a man by the name of Fried, a famous performer, and, and several others, names that probably don't mean much anymore.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The-- yeah, I can't think of it right now.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But there were, were several, yeah, which--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the performance of the 'Elijah' particularly-- well, as I said, we were wondering why this was allowed to be performed.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not only that it was, based under the racial laws, a Jewish composer, it was also, it was also the text that's based on the Old Testament of the prophet Elijah.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's a very controversial text.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It, it, it, it shows that certain biases in there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, about 200-- a little over 200 maybe, a huge choir, beautiful choir.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And our little conductor-- I say our little one.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was even smaller than I am, a fellow by the name of Karl Fischer who was, at that time, a very, very famous Czech conductor.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was, he was just tremendous.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was tremendous.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I wouldn't really be sure of that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know whether, I don't know whether the conductor wanted to do it and, and maybe suggested it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because he wanted to perform oratories.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And one of them was 'Elijah.' By the way, the Verdi's 'Requiem' was performed by another conductor with the same group.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was so much talent.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Even though we were, we were promised not to be sent away while, while this was going on-- the practicing and the performance-- even so, once in a while you saw some of the choir members had been disappearing.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But there was so much talent.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
